    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but my doctor is always so rushed and i feel like he just dismisses my side effects like they aren't a big deal. i've already looked up everything about st johns wort and it seems really straightforward. if i just taper off the zoloft slowly over a week or two and then start the supplement, would that be a safe way to do it on my own? i just really want to get off the pharmaceutical stuff.",
