    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you but it's just so much stress to find a new doctor just for this. honestly, if i take a very small amount of the zoloft for a couple days to bridge it, then stop completely and move to the st johns wort, wouldn't that basically be the same thing as a doctor's plan? it feels like a lot of extra worry for something that just seems like a natural switch.",
