      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Attempting to self-manage this transition by tapering and switching without medical guidance is not a safe practice. The interaction between Sertraline and St. John's Wort is significant, and even a temporary bridge dose can cause dangerous chemical imbalances. For your safety, I urge you to schedule a brief consultation with a pharmacist; they are experts in drug interactions and can guide you on safe alternatives while you wait for a new appointment.",
